sticker-5596.name: Sticker | Jerry | Antwerp 2022
sticker-5596.description:
This item commemorates the 2022 PGL Antwerp CS:GO Championship.

This sticker can be applied to any weapon you own and can be scraped to look more worn. You can scrape the same sticker multiple times, making it a bit more worn each time, until it is removed from the weapon.

This sticker was autographed by professional player Andrey Mekrhyakov playing for forZe eSports at the PGL Antwerp 2022 CS:GO Major Championship.

This glitter sticker was autographed by professional player Mathieu Herbaut playing for Vitality at the PGL Antwerp 2022 CS:GO Major Championship.
